CATION> <LOCATION> Europe </LOCATION>? Yes: 42. No: 47. DK-NA: 10. 12. Should the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> significantly reduce its military spending because of reduced tensions between the <LOCATION> Soviet </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Union </LOCATION> and the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, or not? Yes: 41. No: 52. DK-NA: 7. 13. Do you think the Soviets can be trusted to live up to their arms control agreements? Yes: 30. No: 53. DK-NA: 18. 14. Do you think the <LOCATION> Soviet </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Union </LOCATION> is trying to dominate the world, or do n't you think so? Yes: 35. No: 57. DK-NA: 8.
