rom 2.0100; 1,311.50 Italian lire, down from 1,315.50; 1.1632 Canadian dollars, down from 1.1658. Gold fell in <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> to a late bid price of $ 410.60 a troy ounce, down from $ 412.50 late Wednesday. In <LOCATION> Zurich </LOCATION>, the metal fell to a closing bid of $ 409.50, down from $ 411.70 late Wednesday. Earlier, in <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION>, gold fell $ 5.59 to close at a bid $ 405.76. Silver fell in <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> to a late bid price of $ 5.64 a troy ounce, down from $ 5.65 late Wednesday.
